  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nI wanted to force a regular sync (so I slightly modified the code to do that until we have #1480). \r\n\r\nI ran into the following exception which I believe is a regression from when we introduced atomic writes.\r\n\r\n```\r\n WARNING  11-21 17:36:26    RegularChainSyncer  Task <coroutine object RegularChainSyncer._import_ready_blocks at 0x7f6262706780> finished unexpectedly: 'DBProxy' object has no attribute 'atomic_batch'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nProbably need to expose `atomic_batch` on the `DBProxy`\r\n",
